attributes.title: Ep. 1 "Politically Correct Dodgeball"
attributes.description: Help make this show happen! Support at  http://www.patreon.com/kindafunnySubscribe to Kinda Funny! http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...Written by Nick ScarpinoAnimation by Dagan MoriartyMusic by Tonedeff - http://www.QN5.comTroy Baker as Principal Walken http://www.twitter.com/TroyBakerVA Additional voices: Kristine Steimer http://www.twitter.com/SteimerDid you watch it? Did you like it? It’s pretty cool, right? Well, thing is, we want to do more of these. In fact, we want to do a whole season. Longer episodes, funnier stories, and a really ridiculous arc that Nick has already plotted. But animation doesn’t come cheap, especially at that caliber. So this month, we’re humbly asking our audience to help us fund an entire season of Kinda Funny: The Animated Series. To do that, we’re going to use all of the money we earn on Kinda Funny's Patreon account for the month of January 2016, including the money that’s already been so kindly donated so far.Follow us on Twitter!Greg - http://www.twitter.com/GameOverGreggyColin - http://www.twitter.com/NoTaxationNick - http://www.twitter.com/Nick_ScarpinoTim - http://www.twitter.com/TimGettysKevin - http://www.twitter.com/KindaFunnyKevin
